Definition: a Roman Catholic system of casuistry that when expert opinions differ an actor can follow any solidly probable opinion that he wishes even though some different opinion might be more probable
Synonyms: adj, pert, probabilistic, casuistry, a, Roman, Catholic, system, of, that, when, expert, opinions, differ, an, actor, can, follow, any, solidly, probable, opinion, he, wishes, even, though, some, different, might, be, more
Category: noun.cognition
